a n\u225\'e1vrh na odvolanie ktor\u233\'e9hoko\u318\'3evek ministra. Na Slovensku toti\u382\'7eto plat\u237\'ed z\u225\'e1sada, \u382\'7ee J\u225\'e1no\u353\'61\u237\'edka si obesia sami. Bohu\u382\'7eia\u318\'3e, v\u225\'e1s tu nechali tak\u233\'e9ho sam\u233\'e9ho, \u382\'7ee nakoniec ani obesi\u357\'65 v\u225\'e1s nem\u225\'e1 kto. }
